title: Mid Season Awards
description:
Mal and Nora rejoin to give out there Mid Season awards! They band together to discuss who the season's MVP is so far, Offensive and Defensive Rookie of the Year, Coach of the Year, and much more!
Host: Mallory Rubin and Nora Princiotti
Producer: Steve Ahlman
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
